# Joseph as chief administrator of Egypt — national famine-management plan.
# Phase artifact: payment-treasury (domain fragment). payment is received for grain and the treasury is updated.
# One admitted PDDL Turtle planning artifact; fragments across all phase
# artifacts merge structurally into ONE combined plan (domain name
# 'joseph-famine' shared by every fragment). Formal planning-to-workflow
# demonstration domain; argues no doctrine, claims no historicity.
@prefix ex: <http://example.org/joseph#> .
@prefix ceng: <urn:chatman:engine#> .

ex:treasury-officials ex:record ex:payment .
ex:buyers ex:pay ex:silver .

ex:payment-treasury ceng:pddlDomain """
(define (domain joseph-famine)
  (:requirements :strips)
  (:predicates
    (grain-allocated ?x)
    (payment-received ?x)
    (treasury-updated ?x))
  (:action receive-payment
    :parameters (?x)
    :precondition (and (grain-allocated ?x))
    :effect (and (payment-received ?x)))
  (:action update-treasury
    :parameters (?x)
    :precondition (and (payment-received ?x))
    :effect (and (treasury-updated ?x))))
""" .
